
## Privacy Policy – NextLife AI

**Last updated:** [11-January-2026]

NextLife AI respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal and health-related information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, store, and protect your data when you use the NextLife AI application.

---

### 1. Information We Collect

We may collect the following types of information:

* Personal information such as name, email address, and account details
* Health-related data uploaded by users, including medical records, reports, and prescriptions
* App usage data to improve performance and user experience
* Device and log information such as device type, operating system, and app version

---

### 2. How We Use Your Information

We use your data to:

* Securely store and organize your medical records
* Provide AI-powered summaries and structured health insights
* Enable features such as health history management, file organization, and calendar tracking
* Improve app functionality, reliability, and user experience
* Communicate important updates related to the app

---

### 3. AI and Data Processing

NextLife AI uses artificial intelligence to analyze user-uploaded medical documents for summarization, organization, and informational purposes only.
AI features are designed to assist users in understanding their data and **do not provide medical diagnosis, treatment, or clinical recommendations**.

---

### 4. Data Storage and Security

User data is stored securely using cloud infrastructure and managed databases.
Currently, NextLife AI uses trusted third-party services such as **Supabase** for authentication and data management, and **cloud storage services (such as AWS)** for secure file storage.

As the platform evolves and user scale increases, data storage and processing infrastructure may transition to other secure cloud providers such as **AWS or Google Cloud Platform (GCP)**.
Appropriate security measures, including access controls and encryption where applicable, are implemented to protect user data against unauthorized access, loss, or misuse.

---

### 5. Data Sharing

NextLife AI does not sell or rent user data.

Data may be shared only:

* To operate essential app functionality using trusted service providers
* When required to comply with legal obligations

All third-party services are selected with security and data protection considerations in mind.

---

### 6. Children’s Privacy

NextLife AI is not intended for children under the age of 13.
We do not knowingly collect personal or health-related data from children.

---

### 7. User Rights

Users may request access, correction, or deletion of their personal data by contacting us using the details below, subject to applicable laws and regulations.

---

### 8. Changes to This Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time.
Any changes will be reflected on this page with an updated revision date.

---

### 9. Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:

**Email:** [nextlife@studioilios.org](mailto:nextlife@studioilios.org)

